<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="run-into">run into</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>撞上；偶然遇见；遇到 (困难等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The driver of a large truck, unable to stop in time, ran into our car. 
大卡车司机没能及时停车，撞上了我们的车。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I ran into Linda and we went to a pub. 
我遇见琳达，然后我们一起去了酒吧。</p><footer>2008 湖北</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When I first learned to write in English, I ran into many difficulties. 
我刚开始学习用英语写作时，遇到了很多困难。</p></div></div>